quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Mi wooɗndirii hoodere si konde fukkiima"
  53,2,"Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaani."
  53,3,"O haalata kadi belaaɗe."
  53,4,"Ndee [Alqur’aanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo bahyateeɗo."
  53,5,"Ko joom semmbe janngini ɗum mbo."
  53,6,"Joom mbaadi yooɗndi o fotondiri."
  53,7,"Hombo woni e jookli toowɗi."
  53,8,"refti o ɓadi o ɓattii."
  53,9,"O woni ɓadiiɗo fotde lahñe ɗiɗe wolla ko ɓuri ɓadaade."
  53,10,"O wahyii e maccuɗo makko ko o wahyii ko."
  53,11,"ɓernde mum fennaani e ko o yi'i ko."
  53,12,"mbele hoɗon njeddandira e mum ko yi'i."
  53,13,"Ko noon tigi o yi'i Jibriir laawol goɗngol."
  53,14,"ka lekki jaaɓi njani sanne(haaɗtirdi)."
  53,15,"ko kiin lekki woni aljanna koɗirɗo."
  53,16,"Nde muurata e lekki jaaɓi-he ko naatata."
  53,17,"Gite ɗe oonñaaki nde njawtaani keerol."
  53,18,"Ko goonga o yi'i e kaawsaaji Alla ɓurɗi he mawnide."
  53,19,"Onon he'eferɓe mbelr on nji'i laata e ujjaa."
  53,20,"E manaata tataɓiija goɗɗo oon ne."
  53,21,"Mbele hina woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo."
  53,22,"ɗuum de wadde ko peccugol ngol nuunɗaani."
  53,23,"ɗi ngonah si wonah inɗe ɗe innuɗon onon e baabiraaɓe mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil ɓe ndewaani si wona sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e maɓɓe ummaade to Joom mu'en."
  53,24,"wolla mbele na woodani neɗɗo ko o wooɗa ko."
  53,25,"Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii ko."
  53,26,"Heewii e maleykaaji e ndeer kammuuji ɗi tefoore majji nafatah hu'unde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonan'de mbo O wela O."